{"lemma":"سَرَجَ","slug":"سَرَجَ","root":"س.ر.ج","root_slug":"س-ر-ج","root_link":"/words/roots/س-ر-ج","pos":"V","pos_camel":"verb","paradigm":[{"role":"past_2ms","form":"سَرَجْتَ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"p","per":"2","gen":"m","num":"s"},{"role":"past_2fs","form":"سَرَجْتِ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"p","per":"2","gen":"f","num":"s"},{"role":"past_2md","form":"سَرَجْتُما","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"p","per":"2","gen":"m","num":"d"},{"role":"past_2mp","form":"سَرَجْتُم","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"p","per":"2","gen":"m","num":"p"},{"role":"past_2fp","form":"سَرَجْتُنَّ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"p","per":"2","gen":"f","num":"p"},{"role":"past_3ms","form":"سَرَجَ","in_corpus":true,"count":1,"asp":"p","per":"3","gen":"m","num":"s"},{"role":"past_3fs","form":"سَرَجَت","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"p","per":"3","gen":"f","num":"s"},{"role":"past_3md","form":"سَرَجا","in_corpus":true,"count":2,"asp":"p","per":"3","gen":"m","num":"d"},{"role":"past_3fd","form":"سَرَجَتا","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"p","per":"3","gen":"f","num":"d"},{"role":"past_3mp","form":"سَرَجُوا","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"p","per":"3","gen":"m","num":"p"},{"role":"past_3fp","form":"سَرَجْنَ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"p","per":"3","gen":"f","num":"p"},{"role":"present_2ms","form":"تَسْرَج","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"2","gen":"m","num":"s"},{"role":"present_2fs","form":"تَسْرَجِينَ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"2","gen":"f","num":"s"},{"role":"present_2fs","form":"تَسْرَجِي","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"2","gen":"f","num":"s"},{"role":"present_2md","form":"تَسْرَجا","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"2","gen":"m","num":"d"},{"role":"present_2md","form":"تَسْرَجانِ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"2","gen":"m","num":"d"},{"role":"present_2mp","form":"تَسْرَجُوا","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"2","gen":"m","num":"p"},{"role":"present_2mp","form":"تَسْرَجُونَ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"2","gen":"m","num":"p"},{"role":"present_2fp","form":"تَسْرَجْنَ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"2","gen":"f","num":"p"},{"role":"present_3ms","form":"يَسْرَج","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"3","gen":"m","num":"s"},{"role":"present_3fs","form":"تَسْرَج","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"3","gen":"f","num":"s"},{"role":"present_3md","form":"يَسْرَجا","in_corpus":true,"count":1,"asp":"i","per":"3","gen":"m","num":"d"},{"role":"present_3md","form":"يَسْرَجانِ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"3","gen":"m","num":"d"},{"role":"present_3fd","form":"تَسْرَجا","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"3","gen":"f","num":"d"},{"role":"present_3fd","form":"تَسْرَجانِ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"3","gen":"f","num":"d"},{"role":"present_3mp","form":"يَسْرَجُوا","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"3","gen":"m","num":"p"},{"role":"present_3mp","form":"يَسْرَجُونَ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"3","gen":"m","num":"p"},{"role":"present_3fp","form":"يَسْرَجْنَ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"3","gen":"f","num":"p"},{"role":"past_1ms","form":"سَرَجْتُ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"p","per":"1","gen":"m","num":"s"},{"role":"past_1mp","form":"سَرَجْنا","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"p","per":"1","gen":"m","num":"p"},{"role":"present_1mp","form":"نَسْرَج","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"1","gen":"m","num":"p"},{"role":"present_1ms","form":"أَسْرَج","in_corpus":true,"count":2,"asp":"i","per":"1","gen":"m","num":"s"}],"frequency_in_corpus":6,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":5,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":7},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n19484"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B3%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%8E%D8%AC%D9%8E"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"saddle"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to plait, to twine"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to lie, to sham"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to saddle"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to saddle"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of سَرَجَ (saraja) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"plural of سِرَاج (sirāj)","tags":["form-of","plural"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Borrowed from Aramaic סַרְגָא (sargā) (in Classical Syriac ܣܰܪܓܳܐ), from סְרַג (srag, “to bind, to plait”) (in Classical Syriac ܣܪܰܓ).\nA theory diffused by Abaev derives the word from Iranian, compare Sogdian [script needed] (sʾγr /⁠sāγr⁠/), Ossetian саргъ (sarǧ), but the Iranic words are, if related, perhaps more likely to come from Arabic, or Aramaic, the existence of which he fails to note; the same assertion is made by Corriente/Pereira/Vicente “in spite of the Syriac”, because “the greater part of the Semitic basic lexicon with respect to horses is introduced into the Middle East by Indo-Europeans”.\nHowever, apart from the fact that camels too bear saddles, that notion is vague on statistical grounds: If one goes through the list of horse tack terms, there are just few, particularly less important terms from this semantical field that can only be presumed to be Iranian, comprising بَرْذَعَة (barḏaʕa, “packsaddle”) and جُوَالَق (juwālaq, “saddlebag”), نَمَط (namaṭ, “a rug laid over a saddle”), رَسَن (rasan, “noseband”). Others like خُرْج (ḵurj, “saddlebag”) and لِجَام (lijām, “bridle”) have only vaguely been claimed to be Iranian and themselves been “reborrowed” into Persian, and have Semitic explanations too, or one has much evidence on one side like one has on the other, so for شِكَال (šikāl, “hobble”). Thus it is here: The correspondence of the Aramaic consonants is regular to those of Arabic شَرَّجَ (šarraja, “to weave around”), as has been indicated already by Fraenkel.\n\nBorrowed from Aramaic סְרַג (srag, “to bind, to plait; to girth; to saddle”) (in Classical Syriac ܣܪܰܓ); in the meaning “to saddle” denominal verb in Arabic. Doublet of شَرَجَ (šaraja, “to put together, to interweave”).\n\nSee the etymology of the corresponding lemma form."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n19484","headword_ar":"سَرَجَ","root":"srj","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (O, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sarojN","text_ar":"سَرْجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TK,) (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He lied;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sarija","text_ar":"سَرِجَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) but the latter is outweighed [in authority]; (TA;) like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sadaja","text_ar":"سَدَجَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (O:) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sr~j","text_ar":"سرّج","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$araja","text_ar":"شَرَجَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (O and K * in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$rj","text_ar":"شرج"},{"kind":"text","text":".) You say, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"takal~ama fulaAnN bikalimapK fasaraja EalayohaA biA^usoruwjapK","text_ar":"تَكَلَّمَ فُلَانٌ بِكَلِمَةٍ فَسَرَجَ عَلَيْهَا بِاُسْرُوجَةٍ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one spoke a word,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sentence, and followed it with a lie"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (O.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saraja Alka*iba","text_ar":"سَرَجَ الكَذِبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sarojN","text_ar":"سَرْجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He forged the lie."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) [See also 2.]       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sarajN","text_ar":"سَرَجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as an inf. n., signifies The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"being bright,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shining."},{"kind":"text","text":"(KL.) ―         -b2-  [And hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sarija","text_ar":"سَرِجَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sarajN","text_ar":"سَرَجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TK,) said of one's face, (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, beautiful:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O:) or, said of a man, (TA,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he was"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, beautiful in his face:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) but said by some, to be post-classical; and by some, to be strange. (TA.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sarajato $aEorahaA","text_ar":"سَرَجَتْ شَعْرَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O, K, TA, but not in the CK,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sr~jt","text_ar":"سرّجت","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA, but not in the O,) [thought by SM to be a mistranscription for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sr~Ht","text_ar":"سرّحت"},{"kind":"text","text":", with the unpointed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"H","text_ar":"ح"},{"kind":"text","text":",]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a woman, O)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"plaited her hair;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K;) like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sajaratohu","text_ar":"سَجَرَتْهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (O.)       -A4-  ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saraja","text_ar":"سَرَجَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", expl. as signifying “"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Ephippio instruxit instravitve"},{"kind":"text","text":"equum ” by Golius and Freytag, by the latter as on the authority of the S and K, I do not find in either of those lexicons, nor in any other. The verb having this meaning is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Asrj","text_ar":"اسرج"},{"kind":"text","text":"only.]"}],"source_refs":["O","K","TK","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}